  "body": "Description: a user of a keycard based status profile can get in an infinite loop when trying to set up a new account and chose himself the derivation path \r\n\r\nReproduction (profile has to be keycard based) :\r\n- create new account \r\n- go to 'edit' in derivation path section \r\n- enter pin code of the keycard \r\n- chose another derivation tree then bip44 one (e.g. ropsten test network tree path)\r\n- come back to bip44 path\r\n- what happens is that the app cannot calculate the derivation paths and shows an infinite loop \r\n\r\nVideo: \r\nhttps://photos.app.goo.gl/N7khnMo4Mm5Mvbfu9\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
